net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base

Interface ColumnType<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - The JDBC-level type of the field

    public interface ColumnType<O>
    A description of the SQL-level properties of a given field.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static ColumnType<Integer> INTEGER
      A signed 32-bit integer column.
      static ColumnType<Integer> INTEGER_INDEX
      A generated 32-bit signed integer index column.
      static ColumnType<Long> LONG
      A signed 64-bit integer column.
      static ColumnType<String> LONG_STRING
      A longish variable-length string column which truncates excess data on write.
      static ColumnType<String> SHORT_STRING
      A short fixed-length string column which truncates excess data on write.
